name: Reinterpretation of Dali's Paranoiac Visage
description: This is Dali's painting "Paranoiac Visage" modified by VQVAE + CLIP. Is it a face? Is it a wall? Is it a house? Are they people? "Paranoiac Visage" has many interpretations, as observing a prism through different angles. When reimagined with a Neural Network, it gains movement and a new prism to look at.
